{"an7.81:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.81 ","an7.81:0.2":"8. Vinayavagga ","an7.81:0.3":"Tatiyavinayadharasobhanasutta ","an7.81:1.1":"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannagato vinayadharo sobhati. ","an7.81:1.2":"Katamehi sattahi? ","an7.81:1.3":"Apattim janati, ","an7.81:1.4":"anapattim janati, ","an7.81:1.5":"lahukam apattim janati, ","an7.81:1.6":"garukam apattim janati, ","an7.81:1.7":"vinaye kho pana thito hoti asamhiro, ","an7.81:1.8":"catunnam jhananam …pe… akasiralabhi, ","an7.81:1.9":"asavanam khaya …pe… sacchikatva upasampajja viharati. ","an7.81:1.10":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannagato vinayadharo sobhati”ti. ","an7.81:1.11":"Sattamam. "}